01:41:08.702 --> 01:41:10.181
Right?

01:41:12.806 --> 01:41:14.183
So-yool...

01:41:18.311 --> 01:41:21.849
You swore! You promised!

01:41:35.128 --> 01:41:41.010
<i>Hurrah for Korean independence!</i>

01:41:44.771 --> 01:41:48.014
<i>Hurrah for independence!</i>

01:43:14.093 --> 01:43:17.666
You whore! Come here!

01:43:48.628 --> 01:43:51.108
There's a whore!

01:43:51.164 --> 01:43:54.634
The commissioner's mistress is here!

01:44:33.539 --> 01:44:37.851
<i>The album by SEO Yeon-hee
has been restored.</i>

01:44:38.144 --> 01:44:40.488
<i>After all these years...</i>

01:44:40.546 --> 01:44:44.961
<i>we'll be able to play,
'Joseon's Heart', tomorrow.</i>

01:44:45.251 --> 01:44:49.222
<i>If anyone out there knows
anything about the singer...</i>

01:44:49.289 --> 01:44:56.002
<i>please call in to our station.
You're listening to Classic Oldies.</i>

01:45:06.940 --> 01:45:08.681
You know SEO Yeon-hee?

01:45:10.410 --> 01:45:13.584
What is your relationship to her?

01:45:16.316 --> 01:45:17.693
It's me.

01:45:17.917 --> 01:45:19.919
I'm SEO Yeon-hee.

01:45:25.325 --> 01:45:29.432
There are a few things I have to confirm.

01:45:30.830 --> 01:45:34.334
It was found at the site of Daesung Agency.

01:45:35.168 --> 01:45:38.149
The press doesn't know yet.

01:45:39.005 --> 01:45:43.977
Could you tell me about
the unreleased song?

01:45:49.649 --> 01:45:57.295
<i>♪ Alone on a barren field ♪</i>

01:45:57.957 --> 01:46:02.804
<i>♪ ...the hushed land ♪</i>

01:46:02.862 --> 01:46:07.106
<i>♪ Oh sorrow ♪</i>

01:46:07.166 --> 01:46:11.342
<i>♪ Now become the storm ♪</i>

01:46:11.404 --> 01:46:16.404
<i>♪ And awaken the sky ♪
♪ with its eyes closed ♪</i>

01:46:45.571 --> 01:46:47.278
SEO Yeon-hee...

01:47:15.001 --> 01:47:18.813
I was curious. I had to come.

01:47:20.006 --> 01:47:21.314
It's you!

01:47:26.345 --> 01:47:30.350
You don't recognize me
or are you pretending not to?

01:47:30.850 --> 01:47:33.228
I recognized you right away.

01:47:41.260 --> 01:47:44.673
That old man died and I got remarried.

01:47:44.831 --> 01:47:49.837
My husband and son
don't know how I lived.

01:47:52.839 --> 01:47:56.810
The Ok-hyang you knew died a long time ago.

01:47:57.877 --> 01:48:01.848
The So-yool I knew must've died too.

01:48:02.915 --> 01:48:06.328
Am I right?

01:48:10.590 --> 01:48:12.433
Don't forget.

01:48:12.959 --> 01:48:18.204
No matter what, just be a good singer.

01:48:29.175 --> 01:48:33.146
I enjoyed the song, Ms. SEO Yeon-hee.

01:49:01.207 --> 01:49:02.207
Madam!

01:49:03.576 --> 01:49:04.577
Madam!

01:49:12.218 --> 01:49:14.220
I have something for you.

01:49:40.246 --> 01:49:42.021
Wait here, madam.

01:50:06.939 --> 01:50:09.283
I think you'll be thrilled.

01:50:11.277 --> 01:50:14.554
<i>JUNG SO-YOOL
LOVE, LIES</i>

01:50:17.450 --> 01:50:19.623
'To my best friend in the world...'

01:50:19.719 --> 01:50:21.255
'JUNG So-yool'.

01:50:21.821 --> 01:50:24.461
This is the same person, right?

01:50:26.959 --> 01:50:29.337
You two must've been very close.

01:50:29.862 --> 01:50:32.138
Have you ever heard this song?

01:50:33.966 --> 01:50:36.503
It's been so long...

01:50:36.736 --> 01:50:38.044
That's true.

01:50:38.237 --> 01:50:42.708
Well, her songs all seem
like your imitations.

01:50:45.044 --> 01:50:47.251
But isn't it odd?

01:50:48.781 --> 01:50:50.761
'Love, Lies'.

01:50:51.951 --> 01:50:54.625
This song is completely different.

01:50:55.688 --> 01:50:59.295
Traditional singing method in a ballad.

01:50:59.358 --> 01:51:00.735
It's sounds so...

01:51:01.327 --> 01:51:02.863
I mean, her voice...

01:51:03.863 --> 01:51:09.108
Every note and every beat
is absolutely perfect.

01:51:10.870 --> 01:51:12.850
But it's so terribly sad.

01:51:13.205 --> 01:51:15.378
Something must've happened to her.

01:51:16.375 --> 01:51:19.618
I can feel her sadness completely.

01:51:20.313 --> 01:51:22.725
It's making me sad again.

01:51:23.716 --> 01:51:27.061
Anyway, it's the best of the best!

01:51:30.723 --> 01:51:36.264
You're much better, of course.

01:51:42.535 --> 01:51:44.845
Why didn't I know...

01:51:46.639 --> 01:51:48.676
How great it was?

01:51:51.811 --> 01:51:54.792
Why didn't I know then?

01:51:57.650 --> 01:51:59.652
Please, madam.

01:52:00.720 --> 01:52:03.826
You'll know when you hear it.

01:52:16.902 --> 01:52:18.677
I'll play the song.

01:52:47.366 --> 01:52:48.366
<i>♪ Lies ♪</i>

