<i>To So-yool.</i>

01:53:13.092 --> 01:53:15.538
<i>I hope you'll forgive me.</i>

01:53:20.599 --> 01:53:24.570
<i>You were as beautiful
as peach blossom.</i>

01:53:24.804 --> 01:53:25.804
<i>♪ Lies ♪</i>

