<i>I don't love you.</i>

01:53:52.865 --> 01:53:54.776
<i>Love.</i>

01:53:55.267 --> 01:53:56.302
<i>Lies.</i>

01:53:58.904 --> 01:54:03.546
<i>I hope you'll forget me,
